CJGRw8g6BCCtZ2RnEk98nLMJ5NwO8FW2DCnUdBD2jRtiqlQ1chuoPdwouyIlClWoDocTlGGGVrxmPyRGM4rjLqlTF_p999n0vBb-edxc5lx-O3uy620kEKyNII26t97cd8QrAIXU2g1VFreXZCEKCImTLQrHuHJmi19lT9RxE44sZH99GpnL-KesgjWAQ4pgjk7s4B704TWOvvEkj_xrd8cys-enf2-LMUIfI1Onod2Cg6HNbwB505nPX_N6ks2dR1XwZ6bhpteHE4AFqRP3lYf4k6ZvyZoVwU2zlbvlZpVkSz4QZJEv90UKPXmk372Xs2bceX1uZVua6m2-bp6RdkZYTUu6xx0RgpOFrCEIY6_M1ygiCOFx2p4d-Ktf6ctQyzhylRlGGtiPlIT58XkWH09aN2Fs0MLS1hgsDFi2baaB8T0cRQTlWwse3uA7kInYjVR2weYiI61Pzdf3_AkcrgV0EyuRHYNt1PIXqK34uNNrQqkD49wVeewPskKRSUDPSyJOcyj3e8MTTYOI1KTsd6rnZbmhchgTh5--F0it-SYPA_gU6-wbtG98lLKjCzr9MzDvhNmFgc-ffeyQaI=\\\\\\\",\\\\\\\"summary\\\\\\\":[{\\\\\\\"type\\\\\\\":\\\\\\\"summary_text\\\\\\\",\\\\\\\"text\\\\\\\":\\\\\\\"**Considering test setup**\\\\\\\\n\\\\\\\\nI’m thinking about whether to set multiplexed to true for the createSession response. It seems like I might need the session fields to be multiplexed, and I should add a test file while considering making it public since the rules say top-level test classes should be public. I also need to remember to add AssertJ imports. \\\\\\\\n\\\\\\\\nI’m contemplating the implications of using Native Image support for gRPC, especially concerning metadata for reflective access in tests.\\\\\\\"},{\\\\\\\"type\\\\\\\":\\\\\\\"summary_text\\\\\\\",\\\\\\\"text\\\\\\\":\\\\\\\"**Evaluating gRPC setup**\\\\\\\\n\\\\\\\\nI’m contemplating whether using Netty is excessive for my needs. I could switch to `io.grpc.inprocess` if the dependencies support it, but I’d have to explicitly add the dependency. Using an in-process server/client avoids the complications of ports and Netty, though I can't supply a channel provider unless the class is public. \\\\\\\\n\\\\\\\\nIt seems that the connection options could add more complexity. Maybe it’s simpler to stick with Netty. I need to consider how to handle session pools and executed dialect queries effectively as well.\\\\\\\"},{\\\\\\\"type\\\\\\\":\\\\\\\"summary_text\\\\\\\",\\\\\\\"text\\\\\\\":\\\\\\\"**Finalizing server connection**\\\\\\\\n\\\\\\\\nI need to close the server after using the pool, and it sounds like using a try/finally block or a try-with-resources approach would be best for managing that. \\\\\\\\n\\\\\\\\nI’m considering using a unique database name to prevent Spanner pool reuse across tests—maybe a UUID would work well for that. The URI with a random port should suffice. I'll also need to ensure I execute the SQL statement properly and assert the ClientSideStatementType. Do I need to set autocommit to false and then back to true?\\\\\\\"},{\\\\\\\"type\\\\\\\":\\\\\\\"summary_text\\\\\\\",\\\\\\\"text\\\\\\\":\\\\\\\"**Reviewing connection setup**\\\\\\\\n\\\\\\\\nI'm considering how the `ConnectionImpl` constructor uses `getDialect` in the connection state supplier. It looks like it calls `getDefaultIsolationLevel` but doesn't use a parser at that point. Then, the execute method calls the parser. Should I add a dedicated class for a one-to-one relationship here? I'm thinking about whether we should remove the placeholder or leave it in place. It's a bit unclear, so I need to weigh my options!\\\\\\\"}]}\\\"}, {\\\"type\\\": \\\"toolCall\\\", \\\"id\\\": \\\"call_Jwhx7K8KfbHA86YYEJAgUR6I|fc_0072a0aaf99decd50169f778b6f4a481979c36b6a337ca66ef\\\", \\\"name\\\": \\\"write\\\", \\\"arguments\\\": {\\\"path\\\": \\\"tests/src/com.google.cloud/google-cloud-spanner/6.116.1/src/test/java/com_google_cloud/google_cloud_spanner/ClientSideStatementSetExecutorTest.java\\\", \\\"content\\\": \\\"/*\\\\n * Copyright and related rights waived via CC0\\\\n *\\\\n * You should have received a copy of the CC0 legalcode along with this\\\\n * work. If not, see <http://creativecommons.org/publicdomain/zero/1.0/>.\\\\n */\\\\npackage com_google_cloud.google_cloud_spanner;\\\\n\\\\nimport static org.assertj.core.api.Assertions.assertThat;\\\\n\\\\nimport com.google.cloud.spanner.Statement;\\\\nimport com.google.cloud.spanner.connection.Connection;\\\\nimport com.google.cloud.spanner.connection.ConnectionOptions;\\\\nimport com.google.cloud.spanner.connection.SpannerPool;\\\\nimport com.google.cloud.spanner.connection.StatementResult;\\\\nimport com.google.protobuf.Empty;\\\\nimport com.google.protobuf.Value;\\\\nimport com.google.spanner.v1.CreateSessionRequest;\\\\nimport com.google.spanner.v1.DeleteSessionRequest;\\\\nimport com.google.spanner.v1.ExecuteSqlRequest;\\\\nimport com.google.spanner.v1.PartialResultSet;\\\\nimport com.google.spanner.v1.ResultSetMetadata;\\\\nimport com.google.spanner.v1.Session;\\\\nimport com.google.spanner.v1.SpannerGrpc;\\\\nimport com.google.spanner.v1.StructType;\\\\nimport com.google.spanner.v1.Type;\\\\nimport com.google.spanner.v1.TypeCode;\\\\nimport io.grpc.Server;\\\\nimport io.grpc.ServerBuilder;\\\\nimport io.grpc.Status;\\\\nimport io.grpc.stub.StreamObserver;\\\\nimport java.util.concurrent.TimeUnit;\\\\nimport org.junit.jupiter.api.Test;\\\\n\\\\npublic class ClientSideStatementSetExecutorTest {\\\\n    @Test\\\\n    void executesSetStatementsWithOneAndTwoExecutorParameters() throws Exception {\\\\n        Server server = ServerBuilder.forPort(0).addService(new DialectSpannerService()).build().start();\\\\n        try {\\\\n            ConnectionOptions options =\\\\n                    ConnectionOptions.newBuilder()\\\\n                            .setUri(\\\\n                                    String.format(\\\\n                                            \\\\\\\"cloudspanner://localhost:%d/projects/p/instances/i/databases/d\\\\\\\"\\\\n                                                    + \\\\\\\"?usePlainText=true;trackConnectionLeaks=false;trackSessionLeaks=false\\\\\\\"\\\\n                                                    + \\\\\\\";numChannels=1;minSessions=0;maxSessions=1\\\\\\\",\\\\n                                            server.getPort()))\\\\n                            .build();\\\\n\\\\n            try (Connection connection = options.getConnection()) {\\\\n                assertNoResult(\\\\n                        connection.execute(Statement.of(\\\\\\\"set autocommit = false\\\\\\\")),\\\\n                        StatementResult.ClientSideStatementType.SET_AUTOCOMMIT);\\\\n                assertThat(connection.isAutocommit()).isFalse();\\\\n\\\\n                assertNoResult(\\\\n                        connection.execute(Statement.of(\\\\\\\"set retry_aborts_internally = false\\\\\\\")),\\\\n                        StatementResult.ClientSideStatementType.SET_RETRY_ABORTS_INTERNALLY);\\\\n                assertThat(connection.isRetryAbortsInternally()).isFalse();\\\\n            } finally {\\\\n                SpannerPool.closeSpannerPool();\\\\n            }\\\\n        } finally {\\\\n            server.shutdownNow();\\\\n            assertThat(server.awaitTermination(5, TimeUnit.SECONDS)).isTrue();\\\\n        }\\\\n    }\\\\n\\\\n    private static void assertNoResult(\\\\n            StatementResult result, StatementResult.ClientSideStatementType statementType) {\\\\n        assertThat(result.getResultType()).isEqualTo(StatementResult.ResultType.NO_RESULT);\\\\n        assertThat(result.getClientSideStatementType()).isEqualTo(statementType);\\\\n    }\\\\n\\\\n    private static final class DialectSpannerService extends SpannerGrpc.SpannerImplBase {\\\\n        private static final String DIALECT_SQL_PREFIX = \\\\\\\"select option_value from information_schema.database_options\\\\\\\";\\\\n\\\\n        @Override\\\\n        public void createSession(CreateSessionRequest request, StreamObserver<Session> responseObserver) {\\\\n            responseObserver.onNext(\\\\n                    Session.newBuilder()\\\\n                            .setName(request.getDatabase() + \\\\\\\"/sessions/test-session\\\\\\\")\\\\n                            .setMultiplexed(true)\\\\n                            .build());\\\\n            responseObserver.onCompleted();\\\\n        }\\\\n\\\\n        @Override\\\\n        public void deleteSession(DeleteSessionRequest request, StreamObserver<Empty> responseObserver) {\\\\n            responseObserver.onNext(Empty.getDefaultInstance());\\\\n            responseObserver.onCompleted();\\\\n        }\\\\n\\\\n        @Override\\\\n        public void executeStreamingSql(\\\\n                ExecuteSqlRequest request, StreamObserver<PartialResultSet> responseObserver) {\\\\n            if (!request.getSql().toLowerCase().startsWith(DIALECT_SQL_PREFIX)) {\\\\n                responseObserver.onError(\\\\n                        Status.UNIMPLEMENTED\\\\n                                .withDescription(\\\\\\\"Unexpected SQL: \\\\\\\" + request.getSql())\\\\n                                .asRuntimeException());\\\\n                return;\\\\n            }\\\\n            responseObserver.onNext(\\\\n                    PartialResultSet.newBuilder()\\\\n                            .setMetadata(\\\\n                                    ResultSetMetadata.newBuilder()\\\\n                                            .setRowType(\\\\n                                                    StructType.newBuilder()\\\\n                                                            .addFields(\\\\n                                                                    StructType.Field.newBuilder()\\\\n                                                                            .setName(\\\\\\\"option_value\\\\\\\")\\\\n                                                                            .setType(\\\\n                                                                                    Type.newBuilder()\\\\n                                                                                            .setCode(TypeCode.STRING)\\\\n                                                                                            .build())\\\\n                                                                            .build())\\\\n                                                            .build())\\\\n                                            .build())\\\\n                            .addValues(Value.newBuilder().setStringValue(\\\\\\\"GOOGLE_STANDARD_SQL\\\\\\\").build())\\\\n                            .build());\\\\n            responseObserver.onCompleted();\\\\n        }\\\\n    }\\\\n}\\\\n\\\"}}], \\\"api\\\": \\\"openai-responses\\\", \\\"provider\\\": \\\"OCA\\\", \\\"model\\\": \\\"gpt-5.5\\\", \\\"usage\\\": {\\\"input\\\": 643, \\\"output\\\": 2223, \\\"cacheRead\\\": 108032, \\\"cacheWrite\\\": 0, \\\"totalTokens\\\": 110898, \\\"cost\\\": {\\\"input\\\": 0, \\\"output\\\": 0, \\\"cacheRead\\\": 0, \\\"cacheWrite\\\": 0, \\\"total\\\": 0}}, \\\"stopReason\\\": \\\"toolUse\\\", \\\"timestamp\\\": 1777825954430, \\\"responseId\\\": \\\"resp_0072a0aaf99decd50169f778a33e18819794206f7af5762903\\\"}}\\n8135:[tool-exec] start id=call_Jwhx7K8KfbHA86YYEJAgUR6I|fc_0072a0aaf99decd50169f778b6f4a481979c36b6a337ca66ef name=write args={\\\"path\\\": \\\"tests/src/com.google.cloud/google-cloud-spanner/6.116.1/src/test/java/com_google_cloud/google_cloud_spanner/ClientSideStatementSetExecutorTest.java\\\", \\\"content\\\": \\\"/*\\\\n * Copyright and related rights waived via CC0\\\\n *\\\\n * You should have received a copy of the CC0 legalcode along with this\\\\n * work. If not, see <http://creativecommons.org/publicdomain/zero/1.0/>.\\\\n */\\\\npackage com_google_cloud.google_cloud_spanner;\\\\n\\\\nimport static org.assertj.core.api.Assertions.assertThat;\\\\n\\\\nimport com.google.cloud.spanner.Statement;\\\\nimport com.google.cloud.spanner.connection.Connection;\\\\nimport com.google.cloud.spanner.connection.ConnectionOptions;\\\\nimport com.google.cloud.spanner.connection.SpannerPool;\\\\nimport com.google.cloud.spanner.connection.StatementResult;\\\\nimport com.google.protobuf.Empty;\\\\nimport com.google.protobuf.Value;\\\\nimport com.google.spanner.v1.CreateSessionRequest;\\\\nimport com.google.spanner.v1.DeleteSessionRequest;\\\\nimport com.google.spanner.v1.ExecuteSqlRequest;\\\\nimport com.google.spanner.v1.PartialResultSet;\\\\nimport com.google.spanner.v1.ResultSetMetadata;\\\\nimport com.google.spanner.v1.Session;\\\\nimport com.google.spanner.v1.SpannerGrpc;\\\\nimport com.google.spanner.v1.StructType;\\\\nimport com.google.spanner.v1.Type;\\\\nimport com.google.spanner.v1.TypeCode;\\\\nimport io.grpc.Server;\\\\nimport io.grpc.ServerBuilder;\\\\nimport io.grpc.Status;\\\\nimport io.grpc.stub.StreamObserver;\\\\nimport java.util.concurrent.TimeUnit;\\\\nimport org.junit.jupiter.api.Test;\\\\n\\\\npublic class ClientSideStatementSetExecutorTest {\\\\n    @Test\\\\n    void executesSetStatementsWithOneAndTwoExecutorParameters() throws Exception {\\\\n        Server server = ServerBuilder.forPort(0).addService(new DialectSpannerService()).build().start();\\\\n        try {\\\\n            ConnectionOptions options =\\\\n                    ConnectionOptions.newBuilder()\\\\n                            .setUri(\\\\n                                    String.format(\\\\n                                            \\\\\\\"cloudspanner://localhost:%d/projects/p/instances/i/databases/d\\\\\\\"\\\\n                                                    + \\\\\\\"?usePlainText=true;trackConnectionLeaks=false;trackSessionLeaks=false\\\\\\\"\\\\n                                                    + \\\\\\\";numChannels=1;minSessions=0;maxSessions=1\\\\\\\",\\\\n                                            server.getPort()))\\\\n                            .build();\\\\n\\\\n            try (Connection connection = options.getConnection()) {\\\\n                assertNoResult(\\\\n                        connection.execute(Statement.of(\\\\\\\"set autocommit = false\\\\\\\")),\\\\n                        StatementResult.ClientSideStatementType.SET_AUTOCOMMIT);\\\\n                assertThat(connection.isAutocommit()).isFalse();\\\\n\\\\n                assertNoResult(\\\\n                        connection.execute(Statement.of(\\\\\\\"set retry_aborts_internally = false\\\\\\\")),\\\\n                        StatementResult.ClientSideStatementType.SET_RETRY_ABORTS_INTERNALLY);\\\\n                assertThat(connection.isRetryAbortsInternally()).isFalse();\\\\n            } finally {\\\\n                SpannerPool.closeSpannerPool();\\\\n            }\\\\n        } finally {\\\\n            server.shutdownNow();\\\\n            assertThat(server.awaitTermination(5, TimeUnit.SECONDS)).isTrue();\\\\n        }\\\\n    }\\\\n\\\\n    private static void assertNoResult(\\\\n            StatementResult result, StatementResult.ClientSideStatementType statementType) {\\\\n        assertThat(result.getResultType()).isEqualTo(StatementResult.ResultType.NO_RESULT);\\\\n        assertThat(result.getClientSideStatementType()).isEqualTo(statementType);\\\\n    }\\\\n\\\\n    private static final class DialectSpannerService extends SpannerGrpc.SpannerImplBase {\\\\n        private static final String DIALECT_SQL_PREFIX = \\\\\\\"select option_value from information_schema.database_options\\\\\\\";\\\\n\\\\n        @Override\\\\n        public void createSession(CreateSessionRequest request, StreamObserver<Session> responseObserver) {\\\\n            responseObserver.onNext(\\\\n                    Session.newBuilder()\\\\n                            .setName(request.getDatabase() + \\\\\\\"/sessions/test-session\\\\\\\")\\\\n                            .setMultiplexed(true)\\\\n                            .build());\\\\n            responseObserver.onCompleted();\\\\n        }\\\\n\\\\n        @Override\\\\n        public void deleteSession(DeleteSessionRequest request, StreamObserver<Empty> responseObserver) {\\\\n            responseObserver.onNext(Empty.getDefaultInstance());\\\\n            responseObserver.onCompleted();\\\\n        }\\\\n\\\\n        @Override\\\\n        public void executeStreamingSql(\\\\n                ExecuteSqlRequest request, StreamObserver<PartialResultSet> responseObserver) {\\\\n            if (!request.getSql().toLowerCase().startsWith(DIALECT_SQL_PREFIX)) {\\\\n                responseObserver.onError(\\\\n                        Status.UNIMPLEMENTED\\\\n                                .withDescription(\\\\\\\"Unexpected SQL: \\\\\\\" + request.getSql())\\\\n                                .asRuntimeException());\\\\n                return;\\\\n            }\\\\n            responseObserver.onNext(\\\\n                    PartialResultSet.newBuilder()\\\\n                            .setMetadata(\\\\n                                    ResultSetMetadata.newBuilder()\\\\n                                            .setRowType(\\\\n                                                    StructType.newBuilder()\\\\n                                                            .addFields(\\\\n                                                                    StructType.Field.newBuilder()\\\\n                                                                            .setName(\\\\\\\"option_value\\\\\\\")\\\\n                                                                            .setType(\\\\n                                                                                    Type.newBuilder()\\\\n                                                                                            .setCode(TypeCode.STRING)\\\\n                                                                                            .build())\\\\n                                                                            .build())\\\\n                                                            .build())\\\\n                                            .build())\\\\n                            .addValues(Value.newBuilder().setStringValue(\\\\\\\"GOOGLE_STANDARD_SQL\\\\\\\").build())\\\\n                            .build());\\\\n            responseObserver.onCompleted();\\\\n        }\\\\n    }\\\\n}\\\\n\\\"}\\n8138:[recv] {